In the Team Calendars admin page, there's a tab that allows you to rebuild space calendars, which allows you to re-run the migration to calendars in spaces. The tab doesn't currently provide any information about what this'll do or why you'd do it. The current title is *Rebuild Space Calendars*, and the accompanying text is *Rebuild Space Calendars*.

